description: Mixed use development comprising: up to 1,746 Class C3 residential units; up to 1,190 sq.m (GEA) Flexible Class A1, and/or A2, and/or A3, and/or A4; up to 4,462 sq.m (GEA) business space for B1(a) and/or B1(b) and/or B1(c); up to 500 sq.m (GEA) Class D1 for a children's nursery; up to 750 sq.m (GEA) Class D2 for community space and a management facility; up to 992 sq.m (GEA) for two energy centres; associated open space, hard & soft landscaping, car parking & servicing, highways & transport works and ancillary works; with all matters reserved for future approval except for access (Outline Application). In addition to the matters set out above, full details (access, appearance, landscaping, layout, scale) in relation to the first sub-phase, being Parcel 1, located to the north and east of the site for: 459 residential units; a 365 sq.m energy centre; associated open space, hard and soft landscaping, car parking and servicing, highways and transport works and ancillary works.
